      "id": "R1",
      "title": "Resolution 1",
      "text": "For a moment - just a moment - something exists in Arkham. Something ancient and immense. It rips open the sky. It dominates the landscape. Within moments, it is all you can see. All you can think of. It is impossible. Beautiful. Perfect. The end of everything. And certainly the end of you.",
