        "lose_campaign"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "R2",
      "title": "Resolution 2",
      "text": "The flames and screams build to a fever pitch. A sudden blaze burns into the sky, twirling higher and higher. Within moments it has reached the sigil that floats above the town. The sigil begins to burn. But not only the sigil. The sky begins to brown and tear, like the edges of a photograph held to flame. Soon, all above is ash. And then the city. And then you.",
      "steps": [
        "all_killed",
        "lose_campaign"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "R3",
      "title": "Resolution 3",
      "text": "As you close the second portal, a furious scream shakes the sky. You brace for impact, but none comes. The alien monsters that wander the city, no longer linked to their realms, begin to burn away, and the cultists that remain flee in panic.\nYou've done it. The hordes have been fought back and the city is savedâ€¦ for now.",
